cat << EOF
libvdpau-va-gl uses OpenGL under the hood to accelerate drawing 
and scaling and VA-API (if available) to accelerate video decoding. 
For now VA-API is available on some Intel chips, 
and on some AMD video adapters with help of xvba-va-driver. 
OpenGL is available, you know, on systems with OpenGL available.
EOF
